stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> queued : POST /api/jobs
    queued --> dispatched : JobDispatcherService picks up
    dispatched --> processing : Worker acknowledges
    processing --> completed : All artifacts downloaded
    processing --> failed : Artifact download fails / timeout
    dispatched --> failed : Worker unreachable / HTTP error
    queued --> failed : No matching worker / budget exceeded

    completed --> [*]
    failed --> [*]

    note right of dispatched
        Worker URL stored in job record.
        RemoteJobCompletionService polls
        GET /jobs/{job_id}/status every 10s.
    end note

    note right of failed
        R-001: Strict guard — if ANY artifact
        fails to download, entire job fails.
        GPU: Staggered retry (10/30/60/120s)
        on 502/503 before marking failed.
    end note